            "title": "woojong&#x27;s platformer game",
            "summary": "Author: woojong | Date: 4/13 2026 | Tools: Scratch This is my [Project&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<p><strong>Author: woojong</strong><strong><span style=\"color: #fbeeb8;\"> </span>| Date: 4/13 2026</strong><i> </i><strong>| Tools: </strong><span style=\"color: #e67e23;\">Scratch</span></p>\n<p>This is my [Project Name], which is a [type of project, e.g., interactive game, digital story, or simulation]. I created it so that the audience can [explain the main goal or action].</p>\n<div class=\"post__toc\">\n<h3>Table of Contents</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#mcetoc_1jkudj88eem\">Project Brief</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#mcetoc_1jkudkcahet\">Define</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#mcetoc_1jkudj88eeo\">Explore &amp; Ideate</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#mcetoc_1jkudj88eep\">Logic Design</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#mcetoc_1jkudj88eeq\">Build</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#mcetoc_1jkudj88eer\">Test &amp; Repeat (Iterate)</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<h3 id=\"mcetoc_1jkudj88eem\">Project Brief</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>a guy named bob the ninja tries to go to the end of  the course</p>\n</blockquote>\n<hr>\n<h3>Define</h3>\n<h3 id=\"mcetoc_1jkudkcahet\"></h3>\n<p class=\"msg--highlight msg msg--info\"><em>Who is this for? What problem does it solve? What are the constraints?</em></p>\n<ul style=\"list-style-type: square;\">\n<li><strong><span style=\"color: #0097a7;\">Who:</span></strong> This project is designed for scratchers who are curious about platformer games.</li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #2dc26b;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #0097a7;\">What:</span></strong></span> My main challenge was to get the code right and turn it into reality.</li>\n<li><strong><span style=\"color: #2dc26b;\"><span style=\"color: #0097a7;\">Constraints:</span> </span></strong>The user has to press the arrow keys so that they can move the main character. This makes sure the user can play.</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"mcetoc_1jkudj88eeo\">Explore &amp; Ideate</h3>\n<p class=\"msg msg--info\"><em>What ideas did you consider before choosing a direction?</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><span style=\"color: #0097a7;\">Brainstorming: </span></strong>I started by thinking of characters and sketching a plan for how it would look on the screen.</li>\n<li><strong><span style=\"color: #0097a7;\">The layout</span></strong>: I decided that the most important part of the screen would be bob because because he is the thing that moves.</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h3>Logic Design</h3>\n<h3 id=\"mcetoc_1jkudj88eep\"></h3>\n<p class=\"msg msg--info\"><em>How did you plan the structure before building?</em></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"color: #0097a7;\">Logic:</span></strong> I planned for bob to move whenever the user used the arrow keys                                                                                                    (bob)</p>\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"3\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://carnegie-institute-kr.github.io/carnegiestudent13/media/posts/10/gallery/download.png\" data-size=\"980x1796\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://carnegie-institute-kr.github.io/carnegiestudent13/media/posts/10/gallery/download-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1407\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"3\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://carnegie-institute-kr.github.io/carnegiestudent13/media/posts/10/gallery/download-1.png\" data-size=\"980x1796\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://carnegie-institute-kr.github.io/carnegiestudent13/media/posts/10/gallery/download-1-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1407\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://carnegie-institute-kr.github.io/carnegiestudent13/media/posts/10/gallery/download-2.png\" data-size=\"980x1796\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://carnegie-institute-kr.github.io/carnegiestudent13/media/posts/10/gallery/download-2-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1407\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<table class=\"align-center\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; border-style: solid; height: 194.25px;\" border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 48.5625px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 35.4788%; height: 48.5625px;\"><span style=\"color: #124c39;\"><strong>Sprite Appearance</strong></span></td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.6985%; height: 48.5625px;\"><span style=\"color: #124c39;\"><strong>Trigger</strong></span></td>\n<td style=\"width: 30.7737%; height: 48.5625px;\"><span style=\"color: #124c39;\"><strong>Behaviour</strong></span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 48.5625px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 35.4788%; height: 48.5625px;\">look above </td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.6985%; height: 48.5625px;\">arrow keys</td>\n<td style=\"width: 30.7737%; height: 48.5625px;\">moves</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 48.5625px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 35.4788%; height: 48.5625px;\">spikes</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.6985%; height: 48.5625px;\">bob</td>\n<td style=\"width: 30.7737%; height: 48.5625px;\">kills bob</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 48.5625px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 35.4788%; height: 48.5625px;\">fake platforms</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.6985%; height: 48.5625px;\">bob</td>\n<td style=\"width: 30.7737%; height: 48.5625px;\">drops + kills bob</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"mcetoc_1jkudj88eeq\">Build</h3>\n<p class=\"msg msg--info\"><em>What did you make, and what key decisions did you make while building?</em></p>\n<p>I used scratch to build this. I used variables to handle the interaction and define blocks to manage the simpleness.</p>\n<p>I am particularly proud of bob.</p>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"mcetoc_1jkudj88eer\">Test &amp; Repeat (Iterate)</h3>\n<p class=\"msg msg--info\"><em>What didn't work? What did you change, and why?</em></p>\n<p>One thing that didn't work at first was bob flying.</p>\n<p>I changed the code by changing some variables. This worked because I missplaced some variables.</p>\n<p>try my game!</p>\n<div class=\"post__iframe\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" width=\"485\" height=\"402\" src=\"https://scratch.mit.edu/projects/1264862622/embed\" allowtransparency=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></div>",
